
Ranger Help for: signal
=======================

SYNTAX:      signal <target> <message>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   2
BASE SP:     1 sp
SKILL TYPE:  aid

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to use the elements of nature to communicate
with friend or foe. The target must be smart enough to understand the
message, because it will come via a variety of ways. Its use is limited
to targets on the same continent.

